TextEng: Can you speak?
What are you?
You talk, maybe?
What you be?
What happened to you again?
I have found the cure for you.
Why you sick again?
I got cure to save you.
Yes, I will cure you.
You must know where some treasure lies in the forest. Why don't you tell me where first?
Text: 넌 숲 어딘가에 보물이 어디 있는지 알겠지. 먼저 어디 있는지 말해주는 게 어때?

TextEng: No. I think it would be better to kill you.
Ya, me cure you.
You know where gold be hid? Show me first.
Text: 너 금 숨긴 곳 알지? 먼저 보여줘.

TextEng: No. Me decide to kill you.
All right, I guess I'll cure you.
No gold, no cure. I guess you can just suffer and die.
Text: 금 없으면 치료도 없어. 그냥 고통받다 죽어.

TextEng: Okay, me cure you.
No gold, no cure. That the way it is. You just die I guess.
Text: 금 없으면 치료 없어. 그게 현실이야. 그냥 죽는 거야.

TextEng: Now can you show me what happened here?
Text: 이제 여기서 무슨 일이 있었는지 보여줄 수 있어?

TextEng: Now you show me why you attacked.
So that's how they managed to poison you. But why did they want to?
Text: 그렇게 널 독살한 거구나. 그런데 왜 그러려고 한 거야?

TextEng: That's not the part I care about. What were they after?
Text: 그건 내가 관심 있는 부분이 아니야. 뭘 노린 거야?

TextEng: So you be poisoned in sneaky way. Why them do that?
Text: 그래서 너 교활하게 독 당했구나. 왜 그랬어?

TextEng: You already cured. Me want know why poisoned.
Text: 너 이미 치료됐어. 나 왜 독 당했는지 알고 싶어.

TextEng: What was on that stone?
What be on stone?
Relmar, the crazy dwarf!
Go on.
